> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Jodi\" title=\"Jodi\"><img alt=\"Jodi Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/f/f7/Jodi_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Jodi\" title=\"Jodi\">Jodi</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Kent\" title=\"Kent\"><img alt=\"Kent Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/8/86/Kent_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Kent\" title=\"Kent\">Kent</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Krobus\" title=\"Krobus\"><img alt=\"Krobus Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/1/10/Krobus_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Krobus\" title=\"Krobus\">Krobus</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Leah\" title=\"Leah\"><img alt=\"Leah Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/6/6e/Leah_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Leah\" title=\"Leah\">Leah</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Leo\" title=\"Leo\"><img alt=\"Leo Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/3/3d/Leo_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Leo\" title=\"Leo\">Leo</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Lewis\" title=\"Lewis\"><img alt=\"Lewis Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/b/b6/Lewis_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Lewis\" title=\"Lewis\">Lewis</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Linus\" title=\"Linus\"><img alt=\"Linus Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/d/db/Linus_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Linus\" title=\"Linus\">Linus</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Marnie\" title=\"Marnie\"><img alt=\"Marnie Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/d/d4/Marnie_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Marnie\" title=\"Marnie\">Marnie</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Maru\" title=\"Maru\"><img alt=\"Maru Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/2/23/Maru_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Maru\" title=\"Maru\">Maru</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Pam\" title=\"Pam\"><img alt=\"Pam Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/b/b6/Pam_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Pam\" title=\"Pam\">Pam</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Penny\" title=\"Penny\"><img alt=\"Penny Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/b/bc/Penny_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Penny\" title=\"Penny\">Penny</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Pierre\" title=\"Pierre\"><img alt=\"Pierre Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/c/cf/Pierre_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Pierre\" title=\"Pierre\">Pierre</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Robin\" title=\"Robin\"><img alt=\"Robin Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/d/d1/Robin_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Robin\" title=\"Robin\">Robin</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Sam\" title=\"Sam\"><img alt=\"Sam Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/5/52/Sam_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Sam\" title=\"Sam\">Sam</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Sandy\" title=\"Sandy\"><img alt=\"Sandy Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/7/7d/Sandy_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Sandy\" title=\"Sandy\">Sandy</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Shane\" title=\"Shane\"><img alt=\"Shane Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/b/b4/Shane_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Shane\" title=\"Shane\">Shane</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Willy\" title=\"Willy\"><img alt=\"Willy Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/7/73/Willy_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Willy\" title=\"Willy\">Willy</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Wizard\" title=\"Wizard\"><img alt=\"Wizard Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/e/e9/Wizard_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Wizard\" title=\"Wizard\">Wizard</a></span>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Hate\n</th>\n<td><span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Jas\" title=\"Jas\"><img alt=\"Jas Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/6/68/Jas_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Jas\" title=\"Jas\">Jas</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Sebastian\" title=\"Sebastian\"><img alt=\"Sebastian Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/6/6a/Sebastian_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Sebastian\" title=\"Sebastian\">Sebastian</a></span> • <span class=\"no-wrap\"><a href=\"/Vincent\" title=\"Vincent\"><img alt=\"Vincent Icon.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/0/0b/Vincent_Icon.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/Vincent\" title=\"Vincent\">Vincent</a></span>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Bundles\">Bundles</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Juice&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Bundles\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Juice is one of the options for the <span style=\"display:inline; margin-right:0;\"><img alt=\"Bundle Orange.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/95/Bundle_Orange.png/24px-Bundle_Orange.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/9/95/Bundle_Orange.png/36px-Bundle_Orange.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/9/95/Bundle_Orange.png 2x\" /> <a href=\"/Remixed_Bundles#Brewer.27s_Bundle\" title=\"Remixed Bundles\">Brewer's Bundle</a> in the <a href=\"/Remixed_Bundles#Pantry\" title=\"Remixed Bundles\">Pantry (Remixed)</a></span>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recipes\">Recipes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Juice&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Recipes\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Juice is not used in any recipes.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Tailoring\">Tailoring</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Juice&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Tailoring\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Juice is used in the spool of the <a href=\"/2_Willow_Lane#Sewing_Machine\" title=\"2 Willow Lane\">Sewing Machine</a> to create the dyeable <a href=\"/File:Shirt209.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Shirt209.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/a/a3/Shirt209.png/24px-Shirt209.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/a/a3/Shirt209.png 1.5x\" /></a> <a href=\"/Tailoring\" title=\"Tailoring\">Sports Shirt</a>. It can be used in <a href=\"/Dyeing\" title=\"Dyeing\">dyeing</a>, serving as a green dye at the dye pots, located in <a href=\"/Emily\" title=\"Emily\">Emily</a>'s and <a href=\"/Haley\" title=\"Haley\">Haley</a>'s house, <a href=\"/2_Willow_Lane\" title=\"2 Willow Lane\">2 Willow Lane</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quests\">Quests</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Juice&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Quests\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/Pam\" title=\"Pam\">Pam</a> requests 12 Potato Juice in the <a href=\"/Quests#The_Strong_Stuff\" title=\"Quests\">\"The Strong Stuff\"</a> Special Order.</li>\n<li>One Juice is requested by the Raccoon at the <a href=\"/Giant_Stump\" title=\"Giant Stump\">Giant Stump</a> as part of his fourth request. It may also be requested as part of any request starting with the sixth.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Trivia\">Trivia</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Juice&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: Trivia\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Juice sold by the <a href=\"/Traveling_Cart\" title=\"Traveling Cart\">Traveling Cart</a> will not be of any ingredients type, will sell for <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"150\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />150g</span> (or <span style=\"display: none;\">data-sort-value=\"210\"&gt;</span><span class=\"no-wrap\"><img alt=\"Gold.png\" src=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/18px-Gold.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" srcset=\"/mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/27px-Gold.png 1.5x, /mediawiki/images/thumb/1/10/Gold.png/36px-Gold.png 2x\" />210g</span> with the <a href=\"/Skills#Farming\" title=\"Skills\">Artisan Profession</a>), and will restore 75 <a href=\"/Energy\" title=\"Energy\">energy</a> and 33 <a href=\"/Health\" title=\"Health\">health</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Juice&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-juice_energy-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-juice_energy_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">See <samp>ObjectDataDefinition::CreateFlavoredJuice</samp> in the game code.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/mediawiki/index.php?title=Juice&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: History\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.4\" title=\"Version History\">1.4</a>: Can now be used in <a href=\"/Tailoring\" title=\"Tailoring\">Tailoring</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.5\" title=\"Version History\">1.5</a>: Is now an option in the Brewer's Bundle.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.6\" title=\"Version History\">1.6</a>: Inventory icon changed, it is no longer a recolor of the Wine sprite. The new Juice icon now changes color to match the item used to create it. Positive energy Forage can now be made into Juice. Juice is now requested by the Raccoon.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/Version_History#1.6.2\" title=\"Version History\">1.6.2</a>: Health and Energy now scales with base vegetable's values.</li></ul>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" id=\"navbox\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/Artisan_Goods\" title=\"Artisan Goods\">Artisan Goods</a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Bee_House\" title=\"Bee House\">Bee House</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Honey\" title=\"Honey\">Honey</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Cask\" title=\"Cask\">Cask</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Beer\" title=\"Beer\">Beer</a> • <a href=\"/Cheese\" title=\"Cheese\">Cheese</a> • <a href=\"/Goat_Cheese\" title=\"Goat Cheese\">Goat Cheese</a> • <a href=\"/Mead\" title=\"Mead\">Mead</a> • <a href=\"/Pale_Ale\" title=\"Pale Ale\">Pale Ale</a> • <a href=\"/Wine\" title=\"Wine\">Wine</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Cheese_Press\" title=\"Cheese Press\">Cheese Press</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Cheese\" title=\"Cheese\">Cheese</a> • <a href=\"/Goat_Cheese\" title=\"Goat Cheese\">Goat Cheese</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Keg\" title=\"Keg\">Keg</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Beer\" title=\"Beer\">Beer</a> • <a href=\"/Coffee\" title=\"Coffee\">Coffee</a> • <a href=\"/Green_Tea\" title=\"Green Tea\">Green Tea</a> • <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Juice</a> • <a href=\"/Mead\" title=\"Mead\">Mead</a> • <a href=\"/Pale_Ale\" title=\"Pale Ale\">Pale Ale</a> • <a href=\"/Wine\" title=\"Wine\">Wine</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Loom\" title=\"Loom\">Loom</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Cloth\" title=\"Cloth\">Cloth</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Mayonnaise_Machine\" title=\"Mayonnaise Machine\">Mayonnaise Machine</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Dinosaur_Mayonnaise\" title=\"Dinosaur Mayonnaise\">Dinosaur Mayonnaise</a> • <a href=\"/Duck_Mayonnaise\" title=\"Duck Mayonnaise\">Duck Mayonnaise</a> • <a href=\"/Mayonnaise\" title=\"Mayonnaise\">Mayonnaise</a> • <a href=\"/Void_Mayonnaise\" title=\"Void Mayonnaise\">Void Mayonnaise</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Oil_Maker\" title=\"Oil Maker\">Oil Maker</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Oil\" title=\"Oil\">Oil</a> • <a href=\"/Truffle_Oil\" title=\"Truffle Oil\">Truffle Oil</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Preserves_Jar\" title=\"Preserves Jar\">Preserves Jar</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Aged_Roe\" title=\"Aged Roe\">Aged Roe</a> • <a href=\"/Caviar\" title=\"Caviar\">Caviar</a> • <a href=\"/Jellies_and_Pickles\" title=\"Jellies and Pickles\">Jellies and Pickles</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Fish_Smoker\" title=\"Fish Smoker\">Fish Smoker</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Smoked_Fish\" title=\"Smoked Fish\">Smoked Fish</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th><a href=\"/Dehydrator\" title=\"Dehydrator\">Dehydrator</a>\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Dried_Mushrooms\" title=\"Dried Mushrooms\">Dried Mushrooms</a> • <a href=\"/Dried_Fruit\" title=\"Dried Fruit\">Dried Fruit</a> • <a href=\"/Raisins\" title=\"Raisins\">Raisins</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Misc\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/Maple_Syrup\" title=\"Maple Syrup\">Maple Syrup</a> • <a href=\"/Oak_Resin\" title=\"Oak Resin\">Oak Resin</a> • <a href=\"/Pine_Tar\" title=\"Pine Tar\">Pine Tar</a>  • <a href=\"/Mystic_Syrup\" title=\"Mystic Syrup\">Mystic Syrup</a>\n</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260414101241\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.118 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.132 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1372/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 19230/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 2087/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 10/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1182/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.003/7.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 559 KB/50 MB\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   63.502      1 -total\n 57.31%   36.393      1 Template:Infobox\n 20.94%   13.295      1 Template:Description\n 19.25%   12.224      1 Template:GiftsByItem\n 13.90%    8.827      1 Template:Name\n  7.15%    4.541      1 Template:Duration\n  7.01%    4.453      1 Template:Bundle\n  4.86%    3.087      4 Template:History\n  3.31%    2.103      2 Template:Price\n  2.64%    1.675      4 Template:Version\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key enwiki:pcache:idhash:2086-0!canonical and timestamp 20260414101241 and revision id 190319\n -->\n</div>",
      "wikitext": "{{Infobox\n|eng             = Juice\n|source          = [[Artisan Goods]]\n|sellprice       = 2.25 × Base [[Vegetables|Vegetable]] / [[Foraging#Foraged Items|Forage]] Price\n|ingredients     = Any [[Vegetables|vegetable]] (1) (other than [[Wheat]], [[Hops]], & [[Tea Leaves]]) ''or''<br />Any positive energy [[Foraging#Foraged Items|foraged item]] (1) (other than [[:Category:Mushrooms|Mushrooms]])\n|craftingstation = {{Name|Keg}}\n|crafttime       = 6000m (&#8776;4d)\n|quality         = false\n}}\n{{For|a detailed analysis of profit using the Keg|Keg Productivity}}\n'''Juice''' is an [[Artisan Goods|Artisan Good]] made from placing a [[Vegetables|vegetable]] or [[Foraging#Foraged Items|foraged item]] inside a [[Keg]], taking approximately 4 [[Day Cycle|days]]. Its selling price is the base value of the ingredient input multiplied by 2.25 (3.15 with the [[Skills#Farming|Artisan]] profession).\n\nThe [[energy]] and [[health]] restored by Juice is equal to 2 &times; Base Ingredient Value for edible vegetables and foraged items. For inedible vegetables, Juice will restore energy equal to exactly Base [[vegetables|Vegetable]] Value and health equal to 45% Base [[vegetables|Vegetable]] Value.<ref name=\"juice energy\" /> The color of the Juice also depends on the item used.\n\nAlthough [[Wheat]], [[Hops]], and [[Tea Leaves]] are classified as [[vegetables]], when used with a [[Keg]], they produce [[Beer]], [[Pale Ale]], and [[Green Tea]] respectively.\n\nThe following foraged items can be made into Juice: [[Cave Carrot]], [[Dandelion]], [[Ginger]], [[Hazelnut]], [[Leek]], [[Spring Onion]], [[Snow Yam]], [[Wild Horseradish]], and [[Winter Root]].\n\nJuice cannot be put in a [[cask]].\n\n==Gifting==\n{{GiftsByItem\n|like=Robin,Demetrius,Maru,Linus,Pierre,Caroline,Abigail,Alex,George,Evelyn,Lewis,Clint,Penny,Pam,Emily,Haley,Jodi,Kent,Sam,Leah,Shane,Marnie,Elliott,Gus,Dwarf,Wizard,Harvey,Sandy,Willy,Krobus,Leo\n|hate=Sebastian,Jas,Vincent\n}}\n\n==Bundles==\nJuice is one of the options for the {{bundle|brewers||y}}.\n\n==Recipes==\nJuice is not used in any recipes.\n\n==Tailoring==\nJuice is used in the spool of the [[2 Willow Lane#Sewing Machine|Sewing Machine]] to create the dyeable [[File:Shirt209.png|24px]] [[Tailoring|Sports Shirt]]. It can be used in [[dyeing]], serving as a green dye at the dye pots, located in [[Emily]]'s and [[Haley]]'s house, [[2 Willow Lane]].\n\n==Quests==\n*[[Pam]] requests 12 Potato Juice in the [[Quests#The Strong Stuff|\"The Strong Stuff\"]] Special Order.\n*One Juice is requested by the Raccoon at the [[Giant Stump]] as part of his fourth request. It may also be requested as part of any request starting with the sixth.\n\n==Trivia==\nJuice sold by the [[Traveling Cart]] will not be of any ingredients type, will sell for {{Price|150}} (or {{Price|210}} with the [[Skills#Farming|Artisan Profession]]), and will restore 75 [[energy]] and 33 [[health]].\n\n==References==\n<references>\n<ref name=\"juice energy\">See <samp>ObjectDataDefinition::CreateFlavoredJuice</samp> in the game code.</ref>\n</references>\n\n==History==\n{{History|1.4|Can now be used in [[Tailoring]].}}\n{{History|1.5|Is now an option in the Brewer's Bundle.}}\n{{History|1.6|Inventory icon changed, it is no longer a recolor of the Wine sprite. The new Juice icon now changes color to match the item used to create it. Positive energy Forage can now be made into Juice. Juice is now requested by the Raccoon.}}\n{{History|1.6.2|Health and Energy now scales with base vegetable's values.}}\n{{NavboxArtisanGoods}}\n\n[[Category:Artisan Goods]]\n\n[[de:Saft]]\n[[es:Zumo]]\n[[fr:Jus]]\n[[it:Succo]]\n[[ja:ジュース]]\n[[ko:주스]]\n[[hu:Gyümölcslé]]\n[[pt:Suco]]\n[[ru:Сок]]\n[[tr:Meyve Suyu]]\n[[zh:果汁]]"
